  -  2 YEARS OF EXTENDED SUPERVISION;

TERM OF PROBATION:  3 YEARS;

CONDITIONS OF PROBATION:  
*Follow through with any treatment and/or counseling recommended by Agent;
*Any and all conditions deemed appropriate by agent.
*Defendant to provide DNA sample (if not yet previously provided);

